    "English": "An abundant mineral element, found within the geological strata of all rocky worlds. Easily extracted using a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Terrain Manipulator</span>. Create a tunnel anywhere to begin extraction.<br><br>Process in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span> to create <span class=\"name name-technology\">Glass</span>.",
